{"tid":1015901,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"【注意網絡安全】SHECA根證書已經被納入Mozilla證書庫","createTime":"2019-02-10T12:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T13:54:34.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"81d08e2ec2fb5d2af93e0485d6855f9f9e994f91","tid":1015901,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T12:07:49.000Z","msg":"2018年末，Mozilla發布更加安全的網絡安全服務NSS 3.41版本，SHECA（Shanghai Electronic Certification Authority Co., Ltd. 上海市數字證書認證中心）根證書UCA Extended Validation Root 和UCA Global G2 Root 正式納入Mozilla根證書庫，並已在火狐V65更新到瀏覽器中。<br />\n<br />\n這是自NSS 3.34 GDCA TrustAUTH R5 ROOT受信於Mozilla後，國產品牌數字證書再一次被納入NSS。<br />\n<br />\nNSS 3.41更新詳情：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.mozilla.org%2F&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=032bfe87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://developer.mozilla.org/</a> en-US/docs/Mozilla/Projects/ NSS/NSS_3.41_release_notes<br />\n<br />\nUCA Extended Validation Root 證書鏈演示<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://rsaevg1.good.sheca\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frsaevg1.good.sheca&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=689f5137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rsaevg1.good.sheca</a>. com/<br />\n<br />\nUCA Global G2 Root 證書鏈演示網站<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://rsaovg3.good.sheca\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frsaovg3.good.sheca&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=6f27c3f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rsaovg3.good.sheca</a>. com/<br />\n<br />\n小知識：<br />\n<br />\nNSS（Network Security Services）是由Mozilla主導，火狐瀏覽器和其他許多軟件（包括Google Chrome（非Windows平台）、安卓、Apache、Java、Red Hat等）共用的一組支持客戶端和服務器端安全通信服務的跨平台庫，客戶端支持智能卡，而服務器端支持硬件SSL加速。NSS提供了支持安全套接字層(SSL)/傳輸層安全(TLS) 和S/MIME加密庫的一個完整的開源組件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.wongcw.com/2019/02/09/sheca根證書已經被納入mozilla證書庫/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.wongcw.com%2F2019%2F02%2F09%2Fsheca%E6%A0%B9%E8%AD%89%E6%9B%B8%E5%B7%B2%E7%B6%93%E8%A2%AB%E7%B4%8D%E5%85%A5mozilla%E8%AD%89%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%AB%2F&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=c18d0f9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.wongcw.com/2019/02/09/sheca根證書已經被納入mozilla證書庫/</a><br />\n<br />\n//見到自己拆走佢。iOS冇得拆，重要嘢小心國家級MITH"},{"pid":"5b59044e8f0e20fc3df3e38211dabff45fda11f5","tid":1015901,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T12:08:48.000Z","msg":"MITM*"},{"pid":"2f766990e3004ad0a97ef445b908af7762b8d4ea","tid":1015901,"uid":81113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"即係唔用得Firefox <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes20.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes50.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes500.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf19043f327888e2d78ecba5080b023a0f499e9","tid":1015901,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f766990e3004ad0a97ef445b908af7762b8d4ea","tid":1015901,"uid":81113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"即係唔用得Firefox <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes20.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes50.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes500.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T12:31:41.000Z","msg":"將個CA擺去不信任或拆走佢就得，除咗iOS冇得搞之外，其他browser,os都可以自己手動做"},{"pid":"e1d42eeffbc250f61ec49eae01bbd0fd0b6f257a","tid":1015901,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s